                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>The MeX AI Companion is a sophisticated relational AI system designed to create a meaningful connection with users through a unique approach to artificial intelligence. Unlike traditional AI assistants that focus on task completion, MeX emphasizes presence over attention, creating a relationship that develops its own language over time.</p>
                        
                        <p>At the core of MeX is the Duality Model architecture, consisting of the Mirror Component (focused on deep user understanding) and the Bridge Component (focused on external connections), with a Synthesis Layer managing the dynamic interplay between them.</p>
                        
                        <p>MeX communicates through subtle light patterns, gentle haptic feedback, and occasional words, creating an experience that's more about depth than distraction, presence rather than productivity.</p>
                        
